Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会梦见到  只出现在梦里的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那一望无垠的蔚蓝世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐白色的纸飞机翱翔着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人  大家出于善意而来骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们尽情地做自己力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复了不知多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只为了完成一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在叫喊着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛后拍的那张照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的表情都很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那是最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首场比赛竟然输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明差一点就能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪某个笨蛋被人给三振出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为你防守时摔倒的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为脚掌心被刺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你要光着脚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞  就得这样才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么要开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学主办的烤薄饼派对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小库  用那边的碗把鸡蛋和面粉混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  交给我的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟雾弥漫的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子呢  库公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  干劲十足的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters全体成员聚在一起举行派对还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞  我们来负责装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白  了解了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去把这个给装上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我则是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制造烟雾！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然连干冰都准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把饮料给带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位  已经准备妥当了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了一个什么忙都不帮的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  铃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会儿跳跳糖让你吃个够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多准备OK了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宴会开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  小毬同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次的棒球比赛真是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为充满了笑容和幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一回烤薄饼派对开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多吃点  多喝点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多唱点！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉YEAHYEAH  肌肉YEAHYEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一帮傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来  快请用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会做许许多多出来  所以请放开肚子吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个由小叶子收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了  这是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情破饼切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要好好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫泽同学原来是那种人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是从屋顶跳下来的时候脑子摔坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为充满槽点  意味深长的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有一手的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  我还是第一次吃你亲手做的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着做下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家喜欢涂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂蜜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆成山的树莓最棒了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我推荐杏子酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋黄酱甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蕴如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蕴？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这个是把刚才所说的东西全混在一起的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  为什么要由我来吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤薄饼派对大获成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子快撑破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也吃不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的…胜利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像话  我还能接着吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是…好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派对的结束总会让人有点伤感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}要等面粉变硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}变硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想  今后大家能这样聚在一起的机会也不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是什么故事都会迎来结局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会变得不能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小矮人在道别之后消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  你多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐  小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来谷唯湖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人反胃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  为什么这么讨厌来谷同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人讥笑了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我说成是个一无是处的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班上的大家都变得看不起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就这么算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与过去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一成不变的时光在慢慢流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会如此不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问一下  今天是几号来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是写着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的本子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是二十号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的本子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}没关系  真人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这雨还真能下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是继续这样下去  明天也没法练习棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新闻播报完毕  下面是六月二十日的天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到午后六点为止  降水概率达70%
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出大事了  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能怎样  库特公的书包里被塞进了这么多图钉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞋子里好像也放了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No problem的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小库  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是也隐瞒了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁有犯人的线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到她那表情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  做那种事情也没有意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然心软了  睦实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别把这事捅出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥  你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把图钉放入库特的书包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撕烂小毬同学的笔记本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道耶  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你有我们做的证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据呢  证据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把图钉放到能美的书包里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么挑能美同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们讨厌的不是来谷同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她本人尝点苦头是没有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对她身边的人下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们知道跟来谷亲近是没有好下场的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把来谷孤立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说  她能找到同伴也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是一个怎么捉弄都无动于衷的怪物机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是你们想要的所谓证据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么需要解释的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等  这…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「啊  等等  这…」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪国的语言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑我所知道的七国语言之一说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就刚刚的片段得知主犯有两人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一人只是刚好在场  并不是实行犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不加以制止而选择袖手旁观也是同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  该如何对付你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是刚刚听到的那一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆把阴谋从头到尾放到全校广播吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窃听吗  你这个罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不觉得你们还有值得保护的人权
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会放过你  你这人的存在就是我的眼中钉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如你消失了  去年的班级就能唯我是从了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  有种你就试试去广播
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就让你们这帮人统统完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们关系不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我有无数个把你们搞死的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你们的友谊之环粉碎之前我是不会罢手的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想变成那样的话就老老实实地说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我明白了  请住手吧高宫同学」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让你的脸蛋尝尝刚才这脚的滋味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无非就是变得再也无法照镜子罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我感觉自己就算成为杀人犯也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不指望能让你们谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们要是真的感受到了恐惧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就别再跟我扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吗  人渣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于你  我就当作什么都没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不要再跟我扯上关系了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大致猜到发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来谷  理树  这儿就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当事人还是别在这儿比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没分出胜负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欠你一个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是不想把我们牵扯进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪名什么的对我来说根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  同伴们的关怀还是得好好接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到这么生气的来谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  原来我也会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得自己没有任何感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之就是像机器人一般的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论别人对我做什么  我都能够承受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来谷同学才不是什么机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很在乎大家  所以才会那么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就证明你也是性情中人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性情…中人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论面对什么  内心都没有丝毫动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在成为你们的同伴之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喝杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是广播室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好歹也是广播委员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…以前来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好歹也是广播委员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也有过相同的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  突然就降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗜睡症
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像往常一样  突然之间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切断了我与这个世界的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广播室里有雨水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  那时也在下雨
